snippet.title: [4K] Watch SpaceX Catch A Starship Rocket From Space!!! #IFT5
snippet.description:
[TIME SUBJECT TO CHANGE] This is the fifth fully integrated full stack test flight of Starship and the mighty Super Heavy booster, the largest and most powerful rocket to ever fly. It produces over twice as much thrust as the Saturn V that took humans to the moon. 

The goal of the test is to get further along than IFT-4 in June, 2024. If all goes well, Starship will re-enter in the Indian Ocean about 65 minutes after it lifts off from Starbase, TX, on a suborbital trajectory. And perhaps more exciting, this will be the first time SpaceX will be attempting to catch the Super Heavy booster with the launch tower! 

Get your tickets to the Astro Awards!!! January 25/26 in Austin, TX! - http://astroawards.live

Want more information on how exactly they'll catch Super Heavy? WATCH THIS - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pAPt5vbr-YU

Want to know where to watch this live? I made a video on how to visit Starbase and where to watch a launch from - https://youtu.be/aWvHrih-Juk

Learn more about Everyday Astronaut Mission Control by Guinn Partners! - http://guinnpartners.com

snippet.title: 7 Days Overlanding Iceland (Part 1)
snippet.description:
We spent a week driving epic campers to some of Iceland's most remote & beautiful spots! Enjoy part 1 as we drive through rivers & lava fields to see countless volcanos, waterfalls, & glaciers :) Use our link to get $20 off your first AG1 subscription or $49 off when you sign up for a double subscription just like we have! + 5 free travel packs and a bottle of Vitamin D3K2 :) Click: http://drinkag1.com/karaandnate

🚐 We booked this trip with Bliss Mobil - check them out here! https://www.blissmobil.com/ 

Episode 940 | Filmed September 2024 | Iceland

 💳 Here are all of our top credit card recommendations! - https://www.dailydrop.com/credit-cards 

✈️ Want ONE epic email a week with the top travel news? Get  @DailyDrop  ’s free newsletter, weekend round up by clicking here - https://www.dailydrop.com/newsletters/we-re-drooling-over-this-new-elevated-welcome-offer 

📸 Get behind the scenes content on our Instagram! @karaandnate
https://www.instagram.com/karaandnate/ 

🌎 We created @FareDrop to help you score super cheap international flights! Try it risk free and get flight deals up to 80% off ➡️
https://faredrop.app/ytd_220129 

📧 Read our Sunday Summary email to know what goes on between videos -
https://karaandnate.com/sunday-summary/ 

🎶 Here’s where we got all of our copyright free songs used in this episode -
http://bit.ly/epidemic_sound

——————————————————

Who are Kara and Nate?! 
Watch our documentary here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FuFv4iF8wgg&t=1s 

Originally from Nashville, Tennessee, we got married 2013 and were super “normal.” I was a teacher and Nate started a small printing business from the spare bedroom of our apartment. 

We discovered the world of “travel hacking” while planning our honeymoon & became addicted ;)

So after 2 years of obsessively saving $35k and over 2 million miles and points, we sold our cars and apartment and left home January 10, 2016 for a “one year” trip around the world.

Our goal was to see as many places as possible before we ran out of money and went back home to “normal life.” We started this channel to share our experiences with friends and family, but quickly fell in love with living on the road and found a new passion for capturing our travels through video. So we did everything we could to keep going.

4 years later, we achieved our new goal of visiting 100 countries and all 7 continents. We had no plans to slow down, until 2020 forced us to ;) Which is when we bought a converted van to start exploring our own country for the first time!

After ~2 years of van life, we are back to full time international traveling! And now we are in our 9TH YEAR of finding the best adventures the world has to offer :) 

We are incredibly grateful to be able to continue doing something we love every day. 😊🎥🌎 Thank you to everyone who has been a part of our journey!

11:53 surprise northern lights! 
15:11 Day 2
19:15 leaving the pavement behind
23:58 first river crossings
28:16 Day 3
36:04 insane wind speeds

They spent a total of 96 hours on the ground.
These are the stories they encountered.

snippet.title: Dax - "Lonely Dirt Road" (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
[LYRICS BELOW] "Lonely Dirt Road" is a personal song i wrote. Share this with everyone and anyone and let's make an impact. Somebody out there needs this. Love y'all...Thank you.

Click here to listen: 
https://dax.lnk.to/LonelyDirtRoad


Follow DAX: @thatsdax
Shot by: Logan Meis
Produced by: Lex Nour Beats

#lonelydirtroad #dax #dirtroad #driving #manhood 

Lyrics:

When I need space that’s where I go
A place to escape that nobody knows 
Where I feel free to let things go
And face this evil that burdens my soul
I bring my hatred, I pack my pain
All the emotions I cannot explain
It’s where I found God
And filled that whole
It’s he, myself and I
On that lonely dirt road


I needed somewhere to take my mistakes
I didn’t want my family to see me cry
They’ll never know I’m 
carrying all of this weight 
Dealing with the pressure 
of trying to provide
No sign of struggle can show on my face
They ask if I’m OK I just flash them a smile
Fire up that engine to take me away
I’m speeding through emotions with every mile
On that road is where I find my peace
I remember daddy told me about some times like these
On that road is where my minds at ease
I keep driving life away, rejecting change so


When I need space that’s where I go
A place to escape that nobody knows 
Where I feel free to let things go
And face this evil that burdens my soul
I bring my hatred, I pack my pain
All the emotions I cannot explain
It’s where I found God
And filled that whole
It’s he, myself and I
On that lonely dirt road


I tried my best to plant the seeds
And then I watered everything that was in my life
But as a man, the only flowers that you get
Are when you’re 6 feet under on the day you die
I think I feel the pain my father felt
It’s finally sinking in 
looking back all I see is his eyes
He said that house is not a home
Unless you build it on respect 
with some kids and a loving wife
If these walls could talk
I bet they’d say it’s all my fault
That I don’t try hard
That I ain’t man enough
That I ain’t standing up
That I just burn everything 
that my hands touch
If these walls could talk
I bet they’d say I’m to blame
That I’m the one who put myself inside of all of these chains
That my addictive personalities what ran them away
And that I hurt myself by staying quiet
And not explaining I’m broken
In places, I can’t even see
I know there’s gotta be a heaven
Because the hell that’s in me
Is taking a dangerous toll
That I’m paying with all of my soul


When I need space that’s where I go
A place to escape that nobody knows 
Where I feel free to let things go
And face this evil that burdens my soul
I bring my hatred I pack my pain
All the emotions I cannot explain
It’s where I found God
And filled that whole
It’s he, myself and I
On that lonely dirt road

__________________________________________________________________

If you made it this deep you're a real one. Thank you for continuing to allow me to use my platform to make an impact. Your support is appreciated more than you'll ever know and I will continue to prove that with my actions. I'm very excited. 2024 is going to bring our best and most impactful work. I am putting everything into creating pieces we can all be proud of. This is music for the PEOPLE, spread BY THE PEOPLE. Like, comment, share and let's continue to be the change we wish to see in the world.

snippet.title: SURVIVING HURRICANE MILTON - A DEVASTATING STORM EXPERIENCE
snippet.description:
Hurricane Milton is the second major hurricane to strike Florida in two weeks, aggressively spinning up to a Category 5 storm in the Gulf of Mexico before making landfall in Sarasota Wednesday night. Milton brought insurmountable storm surge, flooding rains, and produced countless tornadoes which ravaged throughout Florida. This was our experience in Orlando.

Though we suffered a bit of property damage and a sleepless night, feeling very thankful that was the extent of our damages. Our hearts go out to all those affected on the coast; hopefully this is the last storm we have to deal with this year.

https://www.instagram.com/tmartn

snippet.title: VENEZUELA vs. ARGENTINA [1-1] | RESUMEN | ELIMINATORIAS SUDAMERICANAS | FECHA 9
snippet.description:
#Venezuela #Argentina #eliminatoriassudamericanas #CreeEnGrande #CONMEBOL 

¡Empate en Maturín entre Venezuela y Argentina! 🤝🇻🇪🇦🇷

La Albiceleste y la Vinotinto se repartieron los puntos, tras un aguerrido duelo por la Fecha 9 de las Eliminatorias Sudamericanas para el Mundial 2026. Argentina se mantiene en la punta de la tabla con 19 puntos, y en tanto Venezuela, en la sexta posición momentáneamente, con 11 puntos y reafirma su ilusión de ir por primera vez a un Mundial.

Argentina mantiene el liderato de la tabla con 19 puntos, mientras que Venezuela se ubica en el sexto puesto, con 11, a la espera del resultado de Brasil, este miércoles, en su visita a Chile. La Vinotinto visitará el martes 15 a Paraguay, y por el lado de la Albiceleste, recibirá a Bolivia.

snippet.title: HUGE Magnet VS Copper Sphere - Defying Gravity- Will a Neodymium Magnet Float Inside?
snippet.description:
In this video, I test the interaction between a neodymium magnet and a copper sphere using the principles of Lenz’s Law. By experimenting with this setup, I explore whether a magnet can float or move differently inside the sphere due to the electromagnetic effects. Join me as I walk through the process of building the copper sphere, setting up the experiment, and analyzing the results. This is part of a continuing exploration of how copper and magnets behave together.

Please consider supporting me on Patreon. https://www.patreon.com/user?u=58360840 You'll receive access to Patreon only posts as well as any 3d printing files that I designed.

snippet.title: Alemán, Gera MX - Abran Paso (Video Oficial)
snippet.description:
Alemán, Gera MX - Abran Paso | Video Oficial

Escúchala y guárdala en plataformas

Sigue a Alemán en

› Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/geramx1/
› Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/GERAMX444

Letra / Lyrics

Hey
Siempre mejoro la técnica 
Mi música es única 
Soy un maestro que carga una túnica 
Encima de la montaña fumando la crónica 
Todos los pacientes están viniendo a mi clínica 

Pongo firma rúbrica pa’ firmar contratos
Pero pa’ hacer este disco con sangre hicimo’ un pacto 
Quieren este proyecto tiburones y lagartos 
Porque saben muy bien 
Que si me dan un beat lo parto

Igual que esa coke, esa no se sirve en vaso 
Por esa se matan en la calle a balazos 
Quieren que sea consciente 
Pa’ que ustedes me hagan caso 
Pero ni pedo, mijo, se siguen dando llavazos

Siempre ando bien gris fumándome el hachís 
Nos vamos volando de San Lucas a San Luis 
Como si fuera Wiz, rapeando soy feliz 
Mi flow siempre florece igual que la cannabis

Siempre ando bien gris fumándome el hachís 
Nos vamos volando de San Lucas a San Luis 
Como si fuera Wiz, rapeando soy feliz 
Mi flow siempre florece igual que la cannabis 

Abran paso tomo el mando, Cachorro y Alemalandro
La Homegrown y los Vagos bateando en el mismo bando 
Cuando tú empezaste en esto ya estábamos dominando 
Mil conciertos en bodegas, la calle está facturando 

Venimos de los dos miles, cabrón, somos dos misiles 
No confiamos en tu rostro con lágrimas de reptiles 
Anda, ve y diles contra esta dupla galáctica 
Ancestrales técnicas, este verso es tu lápida 

En corto les da la pálida negociando en la plática 
Recuerdo el primer millón, también mi primera página 
Recuerdo las caídas, los tropiezos, varias lágrimas 
La fama nos sedujo con lujos, fortuna rápida

Siempre ando bien gris fumándome el hachís 
Nos vamos volando de San Lucas a San Luis 
Como si fuera Wiz, rapeando soy feliz 
Mi flow siempre florece igual que la cannabis

Siempre ando bien gris fumándome el hachís 
Nos vamos volando de San Lucas a San Luis 
Como si fuera Wiz, rapeando soy feliz 
Mi flow siempre florece igual que la cannabis

(Siempre ando bien gris)
(Siempre ando bien gris)
(Siempre ando bien gris)
(Siempre ando bien gris)

Hey
Dicen que tengo un estilo bien lleno de filo 
Que les da castigo, no pueden conmigo 
No dejo testigo, siempre tumbando a cualquier enemigo 
Y rápido sigo, siempre lo consigo
Si no lo sé, entonces investigo
La noche trae frío, me cargo abrigo 
Tu-cun, tu-cun siento mi latido

Ando en ambiente, cuido mi gente
Saben que salgo y que pongo la cara 
Fui diferente, mejor atente 
Que la cuenta tiene que estar bien clara 
Verso caliente, wacha este álbum 
Viene a ponerte bien alta la vara 
Todos atentos, prendan sin falla 
¿A esta dupla quién chingados la para?

Alemán
Es el Cachorro, ma
RV
Rich Vagos
Homegrown Mafia
Uh-uh
Oh-oh
Rich Mafia
Rich, Rich, Rich Mafia
Rich, Rich, Rich Mafia

(Siempre ando bien gris fumándome el hachís)
Rich Vagos
(Nos vamos volando de San Lucas a San Luis)
Home-home-homegrown mafia
(Como si fuera Wiz rapeando soy feliz)
Rich Vagos, Rich Mafia
(Mi flow siempre florece igual que la cannabis)
Es la Rich Mafia, es la Rich Mafia

#Alemán #GeraMX #RichMafia #AbranPaso

snippet.title: 2000 Pound Table
snippet.description:
Attempting to build my biggest project yet. A giant timber-framed table with built-in benches. Made with mortise and tenon joinery, half-lap joints, and lots of wood pegs. 
Sandpaper Storage Bin: https://www.blacktailstudio.com/sandpaper-storage-solution
Damascus Marking Knife: https://www.blacktailstudio.com/marking-knife
N3 Nano Finishing: https://n3nano.com/
My Epoxy Workshop: https://www.blacktailstudio.com/the-epoxy-workshop

snippet.title: Season 13: Spellbinder Official Trailer | Overwatch 2
snippet.description:
Transform into the ultimate master of witchcraft with the Mythic Spellbinder Widowmaker skin. Go from potions apprentice to master of witchcraft by unlocking all four levels with the Mythic Prisms earned in the Premium Battle Pass.

Get ready for spine-chilling action in a haunting new Halloween Terror game mode, Junkenstein’s Laboratory–a fast-paced Team Deathmatch where you can enhance your heroes with powerful cursed talent cards.

Good and evil will collide in our newest collaboration, Overwatch 2 x My Hero Academia.

Enjoy new Map updates, Shop Bundles, spooky surprises, and SO much more.

Have a ghoulishly good time when Overwatch 2 Season 13: Spellbinder arrives Oct 15.

Overwatch 2 is free to play for everyone on console & PC!

snippet.title: Joker: Folie À Deux Pitch Meeting
snippet.description:
Step inside the Pitch Meeting that led to Joker: Folie À Deux! 

Subscribe for more Pitch Meetings: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC9Kq-yEt1iYsbUzNOoIRK0g

Joker was kind of a surprise hit in 2019, becoming one of the most massive R-Rated movies of all time on a relatively small budget. Even though that movie was pretty self-contained, the market dictates that there MUST BE A SEQUEL. And here we are. There is one. It exists. And some choices were made.

So check out the pitch meeting that led to Joker: Folie À Deux to find out how it all came together!

Check Out These Other Videos:

The Acolyte Pitch Meeting
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PqwEE6G6zaU

Deadpool & Wolverine Pitch Meeting
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kUrT2UErII8

Our Website
http://screenrant.com/

snippet.title: Dream Theater - Night Terror (Official Video)
snippet.description:
The wait is over! "Night Terror" is out now and it’s the first glimpse into Parasomnia, a special new chapter for us as bandmates and as brothers. 
Pre-order the album here: https://dream-theater.lnk.to/ParasomniaAlbum

We’re excited for you to experience it on February 7, 2025. 

Lyrics:
Spiders seeking shelter
Fading with the dawn
Vanishing at sunrise
As morning light shines on

Sacrificial martyr
Victim dressed in white
Headed for the slaughter
Angels cry for her tonight

To the cross
At the stake
To the lions
On the rack I break
I break

Night terror
Hysteria
Nocturnal trial by fire
Eyes open wide but I can’t see

Mind awake
Body at rest
Drifting through sleep transition
Borderland state
Swimming through waves
Sensory dream condition

Without warning
I fall down the bottomless well
Flesh is crawling
Need to claw my way out of this hell

By the sword
On the wheel
Twisting in the wind
Pierce the silence
With a scream
Why can’t I remember anything?
Anything

Night terror
Hysteria
Nocturnal trial by fire
Eyes open wide but I can’t see

I can’t see

snippet.title: Mario & Luigi: Brothership – Overview Trailer – Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Pre-order Mario & Luigi: Brothership: https://www.nintendo.com/us/store/products/mario-and-luigi-brothership-switch/?utm_source=SW-AA&utm_medium=soytnoa&utm_campaign=N1138-01&utm_id=N1138-01

It’s all hands on deck for a nautical journey full of twists and turns! Learn all about the fractured world of Concordia, the quirky friends and foes you’ll meet, island exploration, bombastic battles, and more! Set sail in the Mario & Luigi: Brothership game, launching exclusively on the Nintendo Switch system November 7, 2024. Pre-orders are available now on Nintendo eShop.

Paid Nintendo Switch Online members* can buy a pair of Nintendo Switch Game Vouchers** for just $99.98 USD. Redeem each one for a digital game in the game voucher catalog to score savings, including pre-orders! Click here for more information: https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/nintendo-switch-game-vouchers/

*Any Nintendo Switch Online membership (sold separately) and Nintendo Account required for online features. Membership auto-renews after initial term at the then-current price unless canceled. Not available in all countries. Internet access required for online features. Terms apply. nintendo.com/switch-online

**Paid Nintendo Switch Online membership required at the time of purchase and redemption of Nintendo Switch Game Vouchers. Nintendo Switch Game Vouchers must be redeemed within 12 months from purchase date, have no cash value, and cannot be transferred, returned, or redeemed for cash. Each Nintendo Switch Game Voucher may be redeemed for one game offered as part of the catalog. To receive promotional value, Nintendo Switch Game Vouchers must be redeemed for two games with a cumulative price that is higher than the purchase price of the Nintendo Switch Game Vouchers. To pre-order a game using a Nintendo Switch Game Voucher, the Nintendo Switch Game Voucher must not expire prior to the game’s launch date. Nintendo Switch Game Vouchers may not be combined with any other sale, discount, or promotional offer unless otherwise specified. Game catalog subject to change.

Visit Nintendo.com for more info: https://www.nintendo.com/us/

snippet.title: Dog found in home rubble during live CBS report
snippet.description:
During a live report on CBS Mornings, Morgan Rynor from CBS News Miami and neighbors in Fort Pierce found a dog in the rubble of a home destroyed from Hurricane Milton. 

The owners sadly died in the storm but the dog survived and got out of the rubble.

snippet.title: Why Hurricanes Are Becoming More Dangerous
snippet.description:
How do big hurricanes form? Neil deGrasse Tyson teams up with meteorologist John Morales to explain how hurricane season works and why Hurricane Milton was different from other storms. 

Check out our second channel, @StarTalkPlus

Get the NEW StarTalk book, 'To Infinity and Beyond: A Journey of Cosmic Discovery' on Amazon: https://amzn.to/3PL0NFn

Support us on Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/startalkradio

FOLLOW or SUBSCRIBE to StarTalk:
Twitter: http://twitter.com/startalkradio
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/StarTalk
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/startalk

About StarTalk: 
Science meets pop culture on StarTalk! Astrophysicist & Hayden Planetarium director Neil deGrasse Tyson, his comic co-hosts, guest celebrities & scientists discuss astronomy, physics, and everything else about life in the universe. Keep Looking Up!

#StarTalk #neildegrassetyson 

Timestamps: 
00:00 - Introduction: John Morales
01:00 - Storm Naming
02:03 - What Causes Hurricane Season
5:35 - Classification & The Saffir-Simpson Scale

9:40 - What Makes Milton Unique
12:49 - Closing

snippet.title: Nintendo Sound Clock: Alarmo – Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Introducing Nintendo Sound Clock: Alarmo, an interactive alarm clock that’s out of the ordinary! Alarmo responds to your body’s movement with game sounds, so you can feel like you’re waking up in the game world itself. Set an alarm inspired by five Nintendo games, with more alarms on the way as free updates as they become available. 

Add some play to the start of your day! 

Learn more: https://www.nintendo.com/us/store/products/nintendo-sound-clock-alarmo-121311/?utm_source=Other&utm_medium=soytnoa&utm_campaign=N0099-01&utm_id=N0099-01?utm_source=Other&utm_medium=soytnoa&utm_campaign=N0099-01&utm_id=N0099-01

For a limited time*, paid Nintendo Switch Online members in the United States and Canada can purchase Alarmo online via the My Nintendo Store before it is available to purchase by the general public. All visitors to the Nintendo New York store can purchase Nintendo Sound Clock: Alarmo in person at launch while supplies last.

*Early access available until early 2025 at the Nintendo NY store and online in the United States and Canada. Nintendo Account and paid Nintendo Switch Online membership required for online purchase during early access period.

Visit Nintendo.com for more info: https://www.nintendo.com/us/

Subscribe for more Nintendo fun: https://goo.gl/HYYsot

snippet.title: The Marías: Tiny Desk Concert
snippet.description:
This Sept. 15 to Oct. 15, NPR Music celebrates artists from all corners of Latinidad with an 'El Tiny' takeover.

Anamaria Sayre | October 9, 2024
Fresh off the release of its latest album Submarine, The Marías have never felt more ready-made for the Tiny Desk. With the first few chimes of the synth and notes from Maria Zardoya’s breathy vocals, the band makes it clear that there’s no better place to bring its bedroom pop style than this slightly bigger space.

The indie band has been skyrocketing over the last few years with classic Spanglish hits like “Cariño” (featured here at the Desk) and a collab on Bad Bunny’s Un Verano Sin Ti. But there’s so much more to the group than the smooth electronic beats and guitar riffs that meet the ear.

Headed by Puerto Rican lead singer Maria Zardoya, who proudly places a Puerto Rican flag on the Desk halfway through the show, there is an authenticity to the group’s lyricism and presentation that pulses just beneath the emotive keys. The band’s performance feels like a soundtrack for a generation that exists in many worlds, and in The Marías Tiny Desk viewers find a new, ethereal, welcoming world to belong to.

SET LIST
“Real Life”
“Only in My Dreams”
“No One Noticed”
“Cariño”

MUSICIANS
María Zardoya: vocals
Josh Conway: drums
Eddie Friedlander: keys
Jesse Perlman: guitar
Gabriel Steiner: keys, percussion
Doron Zounes: bass

TINY DESK TEAM
Producer: Anamaria Sayre
Director/Editor: Maia Stern
Audio Technical Director: Josh Newell
Host/Series Producer: Bobby Carter
Videographers: Maia Stern, Joshua Bryant, Kara Frame, Mitra I. Arthur
Audio Engineer: Josephine Nyounai
Production Assistant: Elle Mannion
Photographer: Michael Zamora
Tiny Desk Team: Hazel Cills, Ashley Pointer
Executive Producer: Suraya Mohamed
Series Creators: Bob Boilen, Stephen Thompson
VP, Visuals and Music: Keith Jenkins

#themarias #nprmusic #tinydesk

snippet.title: Apex Legends: Techno Terror Collection Event Trailer
snippet.description:
Haunt your way through the Outlands with the return of Trick N’ Treat Trios with Revivals and more spine-chilling surprises! Use Copycat Kits to harness the power of other Legends, unleash the Rev Shell Grenade to hunt enemies with wicked precision, and munch on candy for shields, EVO, and Ultimate charge. 

Complete a new Reward Track for Epic Skins for Mirage and the Devotion as you stalk the twilight streets of E-District. Collect all 24 event items before the event ends to summon Pathfinder’s Prestige Skin: Apex Mecha. It’s time to spook the competition, to death!

Want to learn more?: http://x.ea.com/apxl/techno-terror-event

Apex Legends™ is a free-to-play* battle royale game where legendary characters battle for glory, fame, and fortune on the fringes of the Frontier. Play for free now on PlayStation® 4, PlayStation 5, Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S, Nintendo Switch, and PC via EA App, Epic Games Store and Steam: http://x.ea.com/57366.

zh-Hans.title: 《Apex Legends》：科技恐惧收集活动预告片
zh-Hans.description:
"不给糖就捣蛋三人赛携复活回归，同时外域还有更多令人毛骨悚然的惊喜，赶快来捉鬼吧！使用模仿者工具来驾驭其他传奇的力量，释放亡灵脑壳手雷以惊人的精确度猎杀敌人，同时咀嚼糖果以获得护盾、进化和绝招充能。

在电力区域的朦胧街道上漫步，完成全新奖励追踪，赢取幻象和专注轻机枪的史诗级皮肤。在活动结束前收集全部 24 个活动物品，即可获得探路者的威望级皮肤：Apex 机甲。该让竞争对手吓得魂飞魄散了！

pl.title: Apex Legends: Zwiastun wydarzenia kolekcjonerskiego „Techno terror”
pl.description:
"Nawiedzaj Odludzia dzięki powracającym tercetom „Cukierek albo psikus” z odrodzeniami i mrożącym krew w żyłach niespodziankom! Użyj zestawów do kopiowania, aby ujarzmić moc innych legend, rzuć nowy granat „Głowica”, który z upiorną precyzją będzie ścigać twoich wrogów, i jedz cukierki, by naładować swoje tarcze i zdolność specjalną oraz zdobyć punkty ewolucji. 

Ukończ nową mapę nagród, szerząc strach na ulicach Dzielnicy E, by zdobyć epickie skórki Mirage’a i na Devotion. Zbierz wszystkie 24 zabójcze przedmioty z wydarzenia przed jego końcem, aby przywołać prestiżową skórkę Pathfindera „Mech Apex”. Pora przerazić rywali na śmierć!

en.description:
Haunt your way through the Outlands with the return of Trick N’ Treat Trios with Revivals and more spine-chilling surprises! Use Copycat Kits to harness the power of other Legends, unleash the Rev Shell Grenade to hunt enemies with wicked precision, and munch on candy for shields, EVO, and Ultimate charge. 

Complete a new Reward Track for Epic Skins for Mirage and the Devotion as you stalk the twilight streets of E-District. Collect all 24 event items before the event ends to summon Pathfinder’s Prestige Skin: Apex Mecha. It’s time to spook the competition, to death!

ko.description:
"돌아온 트릭 앤 트릿 트리오 회생으로 아웃랜드에 공포를 퍼뜨리고 등골이 오싹한 놀라운 일들을 경험해 보세요! 카피캣 키트로 다른 레전드의 힘을 사용하고, 적을 치밀하게 사냥할 수 있는 레브 셸 수류탄을 발사하세요. 캔디를 먹으면 실드, 이보, 얼티밋 스킬이 충전됩니다. 

E-디스트릭트의 거리를 누비며 새로운 보상 트랙을 완료하여 미라지와 디보션의 에픽 스킨을 획득하세요. 이벤트 종료 전까지 이벤트 아이템 24개를 모두 모아 패스파인더의 프레스티지 스킨 Apex 메카를 소환하세요. 지금이야말로 적을 겁에 질리게 할 때입니다!

Mettez à profit les kits de copie pour exploiter les capacités d'autres Légendes, servez-vous de la grenade aérobombe pour chasser vos ennemis avec une précision implacable et avalez un maximum de bonbons pour gagner des boucliers, de l'ÉVO et une charge d'ultime.

de-DE.description:
"Sorge in den Outlands mit der Rückkehr von ""Süßes-oder-Saures-Trios"" und weiteren schaurigen Überraschungen für Entsetzen! Nutze die Macht anderer Legenden mit Imitationskits, jage Gegner:innen mit der Ortungsgranate mit tödlicher Präzision und vernasche Süßigkeiten, um Schilde, EVO und Ultimativladung zu erhalten.

Sammle alle 24 Event-Objekte vor dem Ende des Events, um Pathfinders Prestige-Skin ""Apex-Mecha"" zu erhalten. Es wird Zeit, die Konkurrenz zu Tode zu erschrecken!

ar.title: فيديو دعائي لحدث مجموعة الرعب التقني في Apex Legends
ar.description:
"شق طريقك عبر آوت لاندز مع عودة المباريات الثلاثية في خدع وحلوى مع عمليات إعادة الإحياء والمزيد من المفاجآت المثيرة! استخدم عدد التقليد للاستفادة من قوة الأساطير الأخرى، وأطلق قذيفة ريف لاصطياد الأعداء بدقة مذهلة، وتناول الحلوى للحصول على الدروع والتطوّر وشحن القدرة القصوى. 

أكمل مسار مكافآت جديد للمظاهر الملحمية لميراج وسلاح Devotion بينما تلاحق الشوارع الليلية في المقاطعة الإلكترونية. اجمع عناصر الحدث الأربعة والعشرين بالكامل قبل أن ينتهي الحدث لاستدعاء مظهر الهيبة لباث فايندر: آلي Apex. لقد حان الوقت لإضافة الخوف المميت إلى المنافسة!

ru.title: Apex Legends — трейлер коллекционного события «Технотеррор»
ru.description:
"Приготовьтесь навести ужас на Внешние земли: вас ждёт возвращение режима «Сладости и гадости втроём» с возрождениями, а также другие леденящие кровь сюрпризы! Используйте наборы «Имитации», чтобы получить силу других легенд. Отправьте в погоню за врагами Рев-снаряд, который будет преследовать их с ужасающей точностью. И не забудьте перекусить конфетами, чтобы получить заряд щитов, EVO-очки и заряд спецумения. 

Отправляйтесь на сумеречные улицы квартала Э и пройдите новую систему наград, чтобы открыть эпический облик Миража и раскраску «Преданности». Соберите все 24 предмета внешнего вида до конца события и призовите престижный облик Патфайндера «Меха Apex». Пора напугать соперников до смерти!

ja.title: 「エーペックスレジェンズ: テクノテラーコレクションイベント」トレーラー
ja.description:
"トリック・アンド・トリート・トリオが復刻し、アウトランズで不吉な影がつきまとう。他にもリバイバルや背筋が凍るサプライズが登場！コピーキャットで他のレジェンドを強化し、レヴミサイルグレネードを放ち凶悪な正確性で敵を撃ち抜き、お菓子をたくさん食べてシールド、進化ポイント、アルティメットのチャージを獲得しよう。

ミラージュとディヴォーションのスーパーレアスキンを獲得できる新しい報酬トラックを完了して、E-Districtの薄明りに照らされた通りを這い回ろう。イベントが終了するまでにイベントアイテム全24種を集めて、パスファインダー用プレステージスキン「Apexメカ」をゲット。競争相手を死ぬほど怖がらせよう！

もっと詳しく知りたい？: http://x.ea.com/apxl/techno-terror-event

「エーペックスレジェンズ™」は、伝説の戦士が集結してフロンティアの辺境で富と栄誉と名声を懸けて戦う、基本プレイ無料*のバトルロイヤルゲーム。基本プレイ無料の本作をPlayStation®4、PlayStation 5、Xbox One、Xbox Series X|S、Nintendo Switch、PC（EA app、Steam、Epic Games Store）で今すぐプレイ: http://x.ea.com/57366

公式YouTubeチャンネルをチェック: http://x.ea.com/56710
公式Xアカウントをフォロー: https://twitter.com/playapex
公式Instagramアカウントをフォロー: https://www.instagram.com/playapex/
公式TikTokアカウントをフォロー: https://www.tiktok.com/@playapex?lang=en

Production Company: Electronic Arts & Dark Burn Creative
Sound Design and Mix: Respawn Entertainment & Mass Audio
All other categories: Electronic Arts & Respawn Entertainment

*適用されるプラットフォームアカウントおよびプラットフォームのサブスクリプション（別売）が必要となる場合があります。永続的なインターネット接続およびEAアカウントが必要となります。年齢制限が適用されます。本ゲームには、ゲーム内のバーチャルアイテムを入手するためにオプションでバーチャル通貨を購入できるゲーム内機能が含まれます。これらの通貨で入手できるアイテムには、ランダムで排出されるゲーム内のバーチャルアイテムも含まれます。"

es-ES.title: Tráiler del evento de colección Terror tecnológico de Apex Legends
es-ES.description:
"¡Siembra el terror a tu paso por las Tierras Salvajes con el regreso de los tríos con trucos y tratos con reanimaciones y otras espeluznantes sorpresas! Usa kits de imitación para asumir el poder de otras leyendas, usa la granada de cabeza bomba para cazar a tus rivales con una precisión diabólica y atibórrate de golosinas para conseguir escudos, Evo y carga definitiva. 

Completa un nuevo registro de recompensas de aspectos épicos para Mirage y la Devotion mientras acechas en las sombrías calles de Electrodistrito. Reúne los 24 elementos cosméticos del evento antes de que este finalice para recibir el aspecto Prestigio Apex mecánico de Pathfinder. ¡Es hora de asustar a tus rivales hasta la muerte!

¿Quieres obtener más información?: http://x.ea.com/apxl/techno-terror-event

Apex Legends™ es un juego de Battle Royale gratuito* donde personajes legendarios se enfrentan para lograr gloria, fama y fortuna en los confines de la Frontera. Juega gratis ya en PlayStation®4, PlayStation®5, Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S, Nintendo Switch™ y PC a través de EA app, Epic Games Store y Steam: http://x.ea.com/57366.

Visita nuestro canal de YouTube: http://x.ea.com/56710.
Síguenos en X: https://twitter.com/playapex.
Síguenos en Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/playapex/.
Síguenos en TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@playapex

Productora: Electronic Arts y Dark Burn Creative
Diseño y mezcla de sonido: Respawn Entertainment y Mass Audio
Resto de categorías: Electronic Arts y Respawn Entertainment

*Podrían ser necesarias una cuenta y una suscripción de la plataforma correspondiente (se venden por separado). Es necesario disponer de una conexión a Internet estable y una Cuenta EA. Sujeto a restricciones de edad. El juego incluye compras opcionales en el juego de moneda virtual que se puede utilizar para adquirir objetos virtuales del juego, incluida una selección aleatoria de estos objetos."

it.title: Apex Legends: Trailer evento collezione Tecno-incubo
it.description:
"Semina il terrore in battaglia con il ritorno della modalità Trio: Dolcetti e scherzetti e altre sorprese da brivido! Usa i kit di emulazione per provare le abilità delle altre leggende, lancia una testata Rev per colpire i nemici con estrema precisione e mangia dolciumi per ricaricare gli scudi, la Ultimate e i punti Evo. 

Completa un nuovo contatore premi per sbloccare skin epiche per Mirage e la Devotion, mentre tormenti i nemici per le oscure vie dell'E-District. Raccogli tutti i 24 oggetti della collezione entro la fine dell'evento per sbloccare ""Robo-Apex"", la nuova skin Prestigio di Pathfinder. È ora di spaventare a morte gli avversari!

Scopri di più: http://x.ea.com/apxl/techno-terror-event

Apex Legends™ è un battle royale gratuito* in cui personaggi leggendari si sfidano per gloria, fama e ricchezza ai margini della Frontiera. Gioca gratis su PlayStation®4, PlayStation®5, Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S, Nintendo Switch e PC tramite EA app, Epic Games Store e Steam: http://x.ea.com/57366.

Dai un'occhiata al nostro canale YouTube: http://x.ea.com/56710.
Seguici su X: https://twitter.com/playapex.
Seguici su Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/playapex/.
Seguici su TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@playapex?lang=en.

Produzione: Electronic Arts e Dark Burn Creative
Progettazione audio e missaggio: Respawn Entertainment e Mass Audio
Tutte le altre categorie: Electronic Arts e Respawn Entertainment

*Potrebbe essere necessario disporre di un abbonamento (venduto separatamente) e di un account per la relativa piattaforma. Richiede un account EA e una connessione a Internet stabile. Si applicano restrizioni di età. Questo gioco include la possibilità di acquistare, all’interno del gioco, tramite denaro reale una valuta virtuale da utilizzare per acquistare oggetti di gioco virtuali, che potrebbero essere attribuiti anche tramite una selezione casuale."

zh-Hant.title: 《Apex 英雄》：科技驚魂收藏活動
zh-Hant.description:
"於復甦模式隨著回歸的討糖又搗蛋三排和更多令人毛骨悚然的驚喜，在邊疆一路神出鬼沒！藉由模仿工具來利用其他英雄的力量、釋放亡靈頭殼手榴彈來邪惡精準地獵殺敵人，並大口咀嚼糖果來為防護罩、進化點和絕招進行充能。

在電流區的暮色街道上鬼祟行動，完成新獎勵路線即可獲得幻象與專注輕機槍的史詩級造型。在活動結束前收集全部 24 款活動道具，就能解鎖探路者的「頂尖機械」威名造型。該讓競爭對手嚇得魂飛魄散了！

想要了解更多內情嗎？請前往：http://x.ea.com/apxl/techno-terror-event

《Apex 英雄》是一款可免費遊玩*的大逃殺遊戲，傳說中的角色們將在邊境的遠處為光榮、名聲與財富而戰。立即在 PlayStation® 4、PlayStation® 5、Xbox One、Xbox Series X|S、Nintendo Switch 以及 PC 上的 EA app、Steam 及 Epic Games Store 上免費遊玩：http://x.ea.com/57366

查看我們的 YouTube 頻道：http://x.ea.com/56710
在 X 上追蹤我們：https://twitter.com/playapex
在 Instagram 上追蹤我們：https://www.instagram.com/playapex/
在 TikTok 上追蹤我們：https://www.tiktok.com/@playapex?lang=en

製作公司：Electronic Arts 與 Dark Burn Creative
聲音設計與混音：Respawn Entertainment 與 Mass Audio
所有其他項目：Electronic Arts 與 Respawn Entertainment

*需要適用的平台帳號以及平台定期服務（另售）。需要擁有持續的網際網路連線和 EA 帳號。有年齡限制。本遊戲包含非必要的可購買虛擬貨幣，這些貨幣可用來取得虛擬遊戲內道具，包括隨機虛擬遊戲內道具。"

snippet.title: 2025 Porsche Spyder RS Review // We Are Now Deaf
snippet.description:
Check out the clothes we’ve been wearing here: https://glnk.io/3vzrq/thethrottlehouse652

The 2025 Porsche Spyder RS ($192,600 starting in Canada, $164,200 starting in the US) is a mid-engine roadster with the same 4.0L flat six engine as found in the 911 GT3. And with that engine comes a screaming 9,000 rpm redline, 493 horsepower through natural aspiration, and a 3.2 second claimed 0-60 mph time. But with softer suspension than a GT4 RS and a removable roof, where does the Spyder RS fit into Porsche’s lineup? And how does it compare to something like a C8 Z06 Corvette? Thomas and James are excited to find out! We hope you enjoy the episode. Subscribe!

Videography: Karston Chong and Daniel Mason
Editing: Karston Chong
Sound: Harrison Dickson, Karston Chong
Magical Genius Logistics Planners: James Engelsman and Joey Alford
Was present: Thomas Holland

snippet.title: Hurricane Milton Evacuation CHAOS Gas Lines, Last Minute Scramble!
snippet.description:
Hurricane Helene's wrath is fresh, but a new storm, Milton, threatens!  With no time to rest, THOUSANDS scramble to evacuate Tampa Bay.  I take you inside the evacuations, the gas shortages and tell you some stories of people caught in the cross hairs.  Meet some determined residents - a few who choose to stay behind, even on sailboats, while others fight to save their homes with sandbags.  And the tough decisions I have to make as my home is dead center in the projected path of Hurricane Milton.

We will be live on @WxChasing during Hurricane Milton so please tune in. 

00:00 Intro, evacuation gridlock
00:13 Gas Problems
01:55 Riding out Hurricanes in a sailboat
04:31 Sandbag chaos
06:52 a hurricane chasing me home

Loco cabrón así me dice que soy
Los plebes andan ondeados si bajan los vidrios un humaderon sale el olor a pura flor
tengo llamadas perdidas mi morra ya varias veces me marcó quiere que ya me regrese pal cantón

Pero me la paso chingon
Van 4 días enfiestado encerrado traigo un loqueron
Un loqueron no es por amor el lokeron

Ay mamá

Pata fondo acelerado bien adiamantado
Traigo el rolexon atrás de mí viene un convoy

Que las bandidas llegarán en calor

Qué vienen morritas de medio millón en el TikTok de lo mejor

snippet.title: Iran threatens new “crushing attack” on Israel after launching more than 180 missiles  | BBC News
snippet.description:
Iran has threatened to carry out a further “crushing attack” on Israel, after firing 180 ballistic missiles at its regional enemy.

The latest warning from Iran came after Israel’s Prime Minister said his country would retaliate for the latest Iranian missile strike.   Mr Netanyahu told his cabinet: “Iran made a big mistake tonight and it will pay for it.”

Iran launched the missiles in retaliation for a series of Israeli airstrikes on Lebanon and its capital Beirut which killed the Hezbollah leader Hassan Nasrallah and other senior commanders of the Iranian-backed militia group. 

Iran’s president, Masoud Pezeshkian, described the missiles fired at Israel as “a decisive response to the aggression of the Zionist regime”.  It’s reported that the order to launch the missiles was made personally by Iran’s supreme leader, Ali Khamenei.

The Iranian attack came after Israel announced a major ground offensive in southern Lebanon. 

Anna Foster in Beirut presents BBC News at Ten reporting by Jon Donnison, Lucy Williamson, Orla Guerin and Sarah Smith. 

Subscribe here: http://bit.ly/1rbfUog

For more news, analysis and features visit: www.bbc.com/news 

#BBCNews

snippet.title: A COMPLETE UNKNOWN | Official Trailer | Searchlight Pictures
snippet.description:
Timothée Chalamet as Bob Dylan in A COMPLETE UNKNOWN, the ballad of a true original. A Film by James Mangold. Co-starring Edward Norton, Elle Fanning, and Monica Barbaro. Only in theaters Christmas Day. #ACompleteUnknown

Set in the influential New York music scene of the early 60s, A COMPLETE UNKNOWN follows 19-year-old Minnesota musician BOB DYLAN’s (Timothée Chalamet) meteoric rise as a folk singer to concert halls and the top of the charts – his songs and mystique becoming a worldwide sensation – culminating in his groundbreaking electric rock and roll performance at the Newport Folk Festival in 1965.

A Film By James Mangold.

Cast: Timothée Chalamet, Edward Norton, Elle Fanning, Monica Barbaro, Boyd Holbrook, Norbert Leo Butz, Dan Fogler, and Scoot McNairy.

snippet.title: Charli xcx: The BRAT Interview | Apple Music
snippet.description:
Charli xcx sits down with Zane Lowe to talk about all things BRAT.

Ironically, she wasn’t planning for this album to break outside the walls of her fan base. In the interview, they explore the story behind the iconic green text cover, the unexpected cultural moment of “brat summer,” and the remix album. She also opens up to Zane about how her life has changed since the release and the challenges of her new perspective on fame.“

snippet.title: Why a Family Left Their House Designed for Category 5 Storm
snippet.description: A Florida family is evacuating due to Hurricane Milton even though they live in a house designed to withstand a Category 5 storm. Their home is constructed with special modifications. The fixtures hold down the roof under extraordinary wind conditions. The most unique hurricane-resistant feature is the rounded design from the walls to the roof. However, Pilates instructor Deborah Rodriguez says her family is taking no chances.

snippet.title: Historic Hurricane Milton Threatens Florida With Catastrophic Damage
snippet.description:
Mandatory evacuations are underway across the west coast of Florida as millions of residents prepare for life-threatening impacts from Hurricane Milton, which continues to rapidly intensify over the warm waters of the Gulf of Mexico. 

On Monday, Milton strengthened into a powerful Category 5 storm with winds of 180 mph. As of early Tuesday morning, Milton had slightly weakened to Category 4 but is forecast to restrengthen and grow in size.

snippet.title: Watch: Iconic Tropicana Las Vegas demolished with breathtaking implosion
snippet.description:
The iconic Tropicana Las Vegas took its final bow with a breathtaking spectacle.

An impressive drone and fireworks show illuminated the Las Vegas skyline, followed by the Tropicana's 22-second-long implosion at 2:30 a.m. PT on Wednesday.

The momentous event marks the next chapter in Las Vegas' legacy of reinvention: the A’s state-of-the-art ballpark and a world-class entertainment resort destination in partnership with Bally’s Corporation.

snippet.title: LIFE UPDATE and COOKING vlog | Hurricane Helene update
snippet.description:
Life has been a little rough around here for the last 3 weeks.  First, we lost our Gracie Lou and then a week and a half later Hurricane Helene came through and knocked out our power for over a week.  Whew.  It's been crazy.  But, we are safe and we are ready to find our new normal.  Today, I'm just catching you up before we make dinner for some friends.  Thank you for checking on us over these last few weeks.  We love you so much.

0:00 Life update
13:38 Killer White Chicken Chili  https://www.mandyinthemaking.com/recipes/instant-pot-killer-white-chicken-chili
18:22 Grandmom's Cornbread  https://www.mandyinthemaking.com/recipes/grandmoms-southern-cornbread

snippet.title: Red Dead Redemption and Undead Nightmare Coming to PC October 29
snippet.description:
For the first time in its storied legacy, John Marston’s beloved journey can be experienced on PC in stunning, new detail, with both Red Dead Redemption and its iconic zombie-horror companion story, Undead Nightmare, arriving to PC on October 29.

In collaboration with Double Eleven, this new version adds PC-specific enhancements including native 4K resolution at up to 144hz on compatible hardware, monitor support for both Ultrawide (21:9) and Super Ultrawide (32:9), HDR10 support, and full keyboard and mouse functionality.

There’s also support for NVIDIA DLSS 3.7 and AMD FSR 3.0 upscaling technologies, NVIDIA DLSS Frame Generation, adjustable draw distances, shadow quality settings, and more.

snippet.title: What Actually Happened in Asheville: A Hurricane Helene Story
snippet.description:
Our Experience During Hurricane Helene
This is firsthand footage captured in Asheville, NC, from Thursday September 25th to Sunday September 29th. 

In this sensitive time, we acknowledge the deep pain many are experiencing. We kindly ask everyone to be mindful of others when commenting. 

As of October 4th, Jillian still has family stranded in Asheville. We recorded this footage to authentically document the situation as it unfolded on the ground and to help spread the word about the catastrophic devastation so more people can help. 

We invite you to join us in praying for and supporting the people affected in Asheville and throughout the states impacted by Helene. 

Ways You Can Help:

- Support the Hawkins Family Featured in This Video as They Rebuild Their Home!
https://www.gofundme.com/f/support-the-hawkins-family-rebuild-their-home

- Old Europe:
https://www.gofundme.com/f/help-rebuild-asheville-and-support-old-europe

- BeLoved Asheville:
  Venmo:  (https://venmo.com/BeLoved-Asheville)  
  PayPal: (https://www.paypal.me/BeLovedAsheville)

- MANNA FoodBank:
 Donate Here (https://donate.mannafoodbank.org)

- Asheville Survival Program: 
  Venmo: @AppMedSolid  
  CashApp: $Streets1de

Why We Were There:

On September 25th, we were en route from Indiana to Charlotte, NC, with plans to spend one night in Asheville. Due to unforeseen circumstances, we found ourselves unexpectedly staying through one of the worst natural disasters in American history.

As Hurricane Helene approached, we began documenting the unfolding events to share the reality on the ground in real time. What started as a simple recording evolved into a short film that felt essential to capture.

We hope this video offers insight into the rapid, chaotic, and disorienting days leading up to and including Hurricane Helene’s landfall. Watching the footage from NC and neighboring areas, we believe our documentation is vital to understanding how this event unfolded and we hope it inspires you to help in whatever way you can. 

Thank you for taking the time to watch our video. Our hearts and prayers go out to all those affected by this disaster, and we will continue to keep everyone in our thoughts.

Ever Upwards and Shine ON,  
N + J

Footage Filmed By: The Bergamot (Jillian Speece & Nathaniel Paul Hoff) 

Video Edited By: 
Nathaniel Paul Hoff 

Additional Editing By: 
Dalton Misner (@daltonmisner) and Molly Elizabeth (@mollyelizabethdesigns) 

More about us:
Music: thebergamot.com
Film: stateoftheunity.com

snippet.title: Lenier - La Tranka de mi País 🇨🇺 (El Taiger)
snippet.description:
Esto no es una canción, son unas palabras, un sentimiento para mi hermano El Taiger (Jose Manuel Carbajal).

Dir. Oscar Films
Artista Gráfico: Pepe Salom

Letra: La Tranka de mi Pais (El Taiger)

Se encienden las velas
Y todos preguntan 
Quien tiene la culpa
Quien tiene la culpa 

Hermano mío para irte
No hay razón ninguna 
Despierta que te necesita
To’ tu gente y la música de Cuba

Yo sé que Dios hará un milagro
Porque el señor lo puede todo 
Para que nunca tu nos dejes solos

Por favor no te vayas 
Echale alas al alma 
Y despierta por favor 

Por favor no te vayas 
Que nos haces falta 
Todavía oir tu voz

No te vayas que el destino
No te ha marcado el final
Quedan cosas por pasar 
A lo largo del camino

Están tu abuela, tus hijos 
Muy lejos de ese hospital
Despiértate de este mal
Sana todo ese dolor
Y háblame matador
Que nadie te va a matar

Si resucitó Jesus 
Ese que la biblia nombra
Levántate que la sombra 
Nunca pagará tu luz

Un guerrero como tu
No muere de esta manera
Tienes una vida entera 
Pa’ ser el mundo feliz
Levántate de raíz
Sana tu herida, tu piel
Que tú siempre vas hacer 
La Tranka de mi país 🇨🇺

SIGUEME EN:

https://www.instagram.com/lenieroficial/
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCKaXzOt7YX--rtEx9I8RhWQ

localized.title: This Is Escalating Too Quickly...
localized.description:
In this video, we explore the severe weather outlook for the coming days, focusing on both thunderstorm risks in the eastern US and multiple tropical systems in the Atlantic. We'll analyze the potential for damaging winds, hail, and isolated tornadoes in the Ohio Valley and western New York/Pennsylvania region, while also providing crucial updates on Hurricane Kirk, Hurricane Leslie, and the approaching Tropical Storm Milton. Stay tuned for detailed forecasts and essential information for residents in affected areas, particularly as Milton poses a growing threat to Florida midweek.
